@WG-Security

More information is needed.  @johnthepro please provide more information about how PowerShell is launched.  The default ExecutionPolicy should be 'RemoteSigned', and we have verified that it is that on a new system.  It may be that you have a profile that is setting ExecutionPolicy for the shell instance.

Please try running pwsh.exe with the '-NoProfile' switch.
